    <string name="helpdesk_support_ready">Our support team is ready to assist you.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_contact_us">Contact Us</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q1">How do I upload a document?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a1">Go to the Upload tab in the main navigation. Select your file, fill in the document details, and tap Upload. The AI will process it automatically.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q2">How does the AI chatbot work?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a2">Once a document is processed, open it and use the chat panel at the bottom. You can ask questions about the document content and the AI will respond based on it. Each document has a message quota.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q3">How do I change my password?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a3">Navigate to Profile → Change Password. Enter your current password and the new one, then tap Save Password.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q4">What is the trial period?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a4">New accounts start with a 15-day free trial. You can see how many days remain in your Profile screen. After the trial you\'ll need to upgrade to a paid plan to continue.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q5">How do I edit my profile information?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a5">Go to Profile → Edit Profile. Update your first name, last name, or username and tap Save Profile.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q6">How do I delete a document?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a6">Open the document from the Documents tab. Tap the delete icon in the top bar and confirm. This action is permanent and cannot be undone.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q7">Why is my document still processing?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a7">AI processing can take up to a few minutes depending on the document size. The status will update automatically. If it takes longer than 10 minutes, try refreshing or contact support.</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_q8">How do I contact support?</string>
    <string name="helpdesk_faq_a8">Use the Contact Us screen to send us a message. You can also reach us at support@scriptumai.com or call +351 253 000 000 during business hours.</string>

